export const messages = {
    allDay: 'All Day',
    previous: '<',
    today: 'Tday',
    next: '>',
    month: 'Mes',
    week: 'Week',
    day: 'Day',
    agenda: 'Agenda',
    date: 'Date',
    time: 'Time',
    event: 'Event',
    noEventsInRange: 'No events in this range',
    showMore: total => `Show + (${total})`
};
